Bootstrap: docker
From: rocker/r-ver:4.0.5

%post
    Rscript -e 'install.packages("tidyverse")'

    apt-get -y autoremove --purge
    apt-get -y clean

%test
    R --version

%environment
    export LC_ALL=C

%runscript
    R

%help
    Based on the Rocker Project's r-ver:4.0.5 Docker image. Ubuntu 20.04 with base R 4.0.5 built with OpenBLAS. See the GitHub repo for more information: https://github.com/rocker-org/rocker-versioned2. Packages installed: tidyverse family
